Twitturse README
================

Twitturse is a small twitter client written in C and using ncurses library.
It's been developped from scratch

Features
--------

Twitturse don't have very much features yet,

* Follow your tweets
* Send a tweet
* And that's all for now...

* GPL License

Install
-------

./configure --prefix=/path/to/install/twitturse
make
make install

(who said it is not a funny way to install ?!)

Bugs
----

For any bugs or feature request visit the BugTracker:
http://bug.nicosphere.net


